<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>loveky的电影院</title>
        <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
        <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
        <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
        </head>
    <body style="padding-top: 60px">
        <div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
            <div class="navbar-inner">
                <div class="container">
                    <a class="brand" href="/">loveky的电影院</a>
                    <% if logged_in? %>
                        <ul class="nav">
                            <li>Hello <a id="username"><%= current_user.username %></a> !</li>
                        </ul>
                    <% end %>
                    <ul class="nav pull-right">
                        <% if logged_in? %>
                            <li><%= link_to "退出", logout_path %></li>
                        <% else %>
                            <li><%= link_to "注册新用户", register_path %></li>
                            <li><%= link_to "登录", login_path %></li>
                        <% end %>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <%= render 'layouts/messages' %>
            <div id="main" class="span9 pull-left">
                <%= yield %>
            </div>
            <div id="sidebar" class="span3 pull-right">
                <div class="sidebar_box">
                    <div class="input-append">
                        <input class="span2" id="appendedInputButton" type="text">
                        <button id="search" class="btn" type="button">搜搜看</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="sidebar_box">
                    本站光荣的采用<a href="http://rubyonrails.org/">Rails</a> + <a href="twitter.github.com/bootstrap/">Bootstrap</a> + <a href="http://jquery.org/">jQuery</a>搭建，感谢<a href="http://www.cloudfoundry.com">CloudFoundry</a>提供免费部署平台。所有数据均来自互联网。网站程序已开源在<a href="https://github.com/loveky/baidu_movie">Github</a>。
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    使用本站过程中如有任何问题，请猛击<a href="https://github.com/loveky/baidu_movie/issues/new">这里</a>提交issue。
                </div>
            </div> 
        </div> 
    </body>
</html>